Rating: 3
This is a great marinade. I had do make do with dried nutmeg and no allspice, but it turned out just fine. I added a little olive oil, which helped to keep the tenderloin I used moist. The marinade did burn rather easily, so I only grilled it part of the way and finished it up in a 400 degree oven, then served it as an entre. My family wants it again next week!

Rating: 4
